---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Core Industry Services | Cyberfyx">
  <section style="padding-top: 100px; padding-bottom: 60px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items: center; gap: 4rem;">
        <div class="fade-up">
          <h1 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Core Industry Services</h1>
          <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-secondary);">Cyberfyx provides end-to-end support—from gap assessments, documentation, training, and internal audits to certification liaison and post-certification maintenance. We ensure that management systems are not just compliant, but also integrated, efficient, and aligned with business performance objectives.</p>
      
        </div>
        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="text-align: center; padding: 4rem;">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-industry" style="font-size: 6rem; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <h2>Our <span class="text-gradient">Offerings</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
        
        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>ISO 9001 – Quality Management System</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">We help organizations establish robust QMS frameworks for consistent product and service delivery. Cyberfyx supports policy development, process mapping, internal audits, and certification readiness.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>ISO 14001 – Environmental Management System</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Cyberfyx enables companies to implement eco-conscious operational controls, perform environmental impact assessments, and maintain regulatory compliance with sustainability goals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>ISO 45001 – Occupational Health & Safety Management System</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">We assist in creating safe work environments by implementing hazard identification, risk mitigation, and safety culture practices aligned with ISO 45001 requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>AS9100 – Aerospace Quality Management</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Tailored for the aerospace sector, Cyberfyx supports the implementation of AS9100 standards with a focus on product safety, risk management, and regulatory alignment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>IATF 16949 – Automotive Quality Management System</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">For the automotive supply chain, Cyberfyx delivers gap assessments, process optimization, and audit support to help organizations meet the quality expectations of OEMs and Tier-1 suppliers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>Fire Safety Audit</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">We assess fire protection systems, evacuation protocols, and risk controls as per NBC and local fire regulations. Cyberfyx ensures your premises meet safety compliance and insurance requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>Forest Stewardship Council (FSC) Audit</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Ensures responsible sourcing and sustainable forest management practices in line with FSC Chain of Custody (CoC) standards. Cyberfyx supports FSC audit readiness, documentation, traceability, and supplier compliance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up delay-100" style="padding: 2.5rem; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-secondary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-secondary);"></i>SEDEX Audit (SMETA)</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">Social compliance audit based on labor rights, health & safety, environment, and business ethics. Cyberfyx helps you prepare for SMETA 2/4-pillar audits and improve your supplier credibility.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-card fade-up" style="grid-column: 1 / -1; padding: 2.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);">
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="font-size: 0.5rem; margin-right: 10px; vertical-align: middle; color: var(--accent-primary);"></i>Awareness & Internal Auditor Training</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem;">We deliver structured training for ISO standards, compliance frameworks, and audit skills. Our programs equip teams to understand requirements and independently conduct internal audits.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to All Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
